'''''Illudium''''' was a [[Lambda-class T-4a shuttle/Legends|Lambda-class T-4a shuttle]] of the same group as [[Tydirium/Legends|''Tydirium'']]. It was found in [[Outpost 327]] when the latter was captured in the [[Mission to Zhar]].

==Behind the scenes==
All the shuttles in the Outpost share names with real-life or fictional elements. "Illudium" is an obscure fictional element mentioned in the [[Wikipedia:Marvin the Martian|''Marvin the Martian'']] cartoons in the form of the "Illudium Q-36 Explosive Space Modulator".

